UFC CEO Dana White said Dillon Danis is prohibited from participating in any future events amid fallout from Saturday's fight with Islam Makhachev’s team at UFC 322.
UFC flyweight contender Brandon Royval ripped the idea of fighting at the White House next year as part of the celebration of the 250th anniversary of the United States.
Former UFC fighter Godofredo Pepey, 38, was found dead in his Florida jail cell Saturday night from an apparent suicide while facing domestic violence charges.
UFC president Dana White confirmed Tuesday that he has been in contact with the FBI after unusual betting patterns emerged before Isaac Dulgarian's shocking first-round loss.
The UFC ct 29-year-old Isaac Dulgarian after betting irregularities surfaced following his submission loss to Yadier del Valle, sparking an integrity investigation.
UFC star Valentina Shevchenko fired back at Ronda Rousey in defense of Joe Rogan after the Hall of Famer took a swipe at the commentator.
Former UFC champion Ronda Rousey took a swipe at Joe Rogan in a recent podcast interview with comedian Bert Kreischer. Rousey is a UFC Hall of Famer.
UFC fighter Bryce Mitchell disavowed President Donald Trump in a scathing rant on Friday, calling him the "Antichrist" in a video posted to social media.
UFC heavyweight champion Tom Aspinall faced criticism for stopping his fight with Ciryl Gane following an eye poke, sparking debate among fans and MMA experts.
UFC ring announcer Bruce Buffer said it was an “honor" to have the opportunity to step inside the Octagon at next year’s UFC event at the White House.
Conor McGregor accepted an 18-month UFC suspension for anti-doping policy violations after missing three biological sample collections in 2024.
UFC CEO Dana White predicted the June 2026 White House fight card will be the "greatest ever assembled," with fighters lobbying to participate in the historic event.
Fox News Digital reviews A24's gritty biopic "The Smashing Machine" starring Dwayne Johnson as MMA fighter Mark Kerr and Emily Blunt as Dawn Staples. In theaters October 3, 2025.
UFC president Dana White took a CBS News reporter on the ride of his wife at a private baccarat table at the Bellagio Hotel and Casino in Las Vegas.
Michael Chandler and Conor McGregor have been chirping for quite some time, but with a UFC event at the White House on the horizon, their fight may finally happen.
UFC president Dana White revealed to "60 Minutes" what he and former President Barack Obama talked about during President Donald Trump's inauguration.
Ultimate Fighting Championship (UFC) CEO Dana White defended UFC’s appeal to young masculine men on the 58th season premiere of “60 Minutes" Sunday night.
Trump supporter Dana White called for unity following Charlie Kirk's assassination, describing his shock at the news and the effect on his college-aged daughter.
Raja Jackson, son of former UFC champ Rampage Jackson, was arrested on felony charges for allegedly assaulting wrestler Stuart Smith in a live-streamed match.
Dana White said the UFC event at the White House marking America’s 250th birthday was President Donald Trump’s idea and will feature fighters walking out of the Oval Office.
Dana White expressed shock over Charlie Kirk's killing during a university debate and said his children were deeply affected by the shooting.
UFC president Dana White argued that fighters prefer to keep their earnings private not due to low pay, but to avoid being approached for handouts.
Elon Musk backed UFC fighter Conor McGregor’s bid for Irish president after officials tried to block his independent run through nomination rules.
UFC President Dana White confirmed Thursday that the White House event for America’s 250th birthday celebration is "on," as new details about the event have been reported.
UFC great Jon Jones was cleared of charges in New Mexico traffic case after prosecutors agreed to dismiss claims the professional fighter left the scene of the crash.
Raja Jackson, the son of former UFC champion Quinton Jackson, took massive heat on Saturday night over an incident at a pro wrestling show over the weekend.
Former NFL fullback Josh Hokit defeated Guilherme Uriel in Dana White's Contender Series in unleashed on the league in a subsequent promo.
Ivanka Trump helps facilitate White House UFC fight planned for July 2026 as part of America250 celebrations marking the nation's semiquincentennial.
A thought appears to be becoming a reality, as Dana White said fights on the White House lawn are "absolutely going to happen" next year.
Former UFC fighter Ben Askren says he found faith after undergoing a double lung transplant last month. The 40-year-old said he felt called to his faith after waking from a coma.
